38379>>>>>    Procedure SetActionButtons
38382>>>>>        tWebNavigateData NavigateData
38382>>>>>        tWebNavigateData NavigateData
38382>>>>>        Boolean bHasRecord
38382>>>>>        Handle hoDD
38382>>>>>
38382>>>>>        Get Server to hoDD
38383>>>>>        Get GetNavigateData to NavigateData
38384>>>>>        Get HasRecord of hoDD to bHasRecord
38385>>>>>
38385>>>>>        // let's hide all buttons and then Show the ones we want
38385>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oEditBtn to False
38386>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oSaveBtn to False
38387>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oCancelChangesBtn to False
38388>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oDeleteBtn to False
38389>>>>>
38389>>>>>        If (NavigateData.bReadOnly) Begin
38391>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oEditBtn to True
38392>>>>>        End
38392>>>>>>
38392>>>>>        Else Begin
38393>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oSaveBtn to True
38394>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oCancelChangesBtn to True
38395>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oDeleteBtn to bHasRecord
38396>>>>>        End
38396>>>>>>
38396>>>>>    End_Procedure
